I guess you can call it that.

1025
01:24:11,275 --> 01:24:14,836
<i>Tor... Jack Begosian. Take the shot.</i>

1026
01:24:17,195 --> 01:24:18,959
<i>Tor, take the shot.</i>

1027
01:24:21,315 --> 01:24:22,805
Tor, take the shot.

1028
