1047
01:26:49,315 --> 01:26:50,726
<i>...Front Street, amateur footage...</i>

1048
01:27:01,275 --> 01:27:02,686
<i>...armed with automatic weapons,</i>

1049
01:27:02,755 --> 01:27:05,804
<i>began a gun battle after a
