1055
01:27:19,395 --> 01:27:25,516
Bruce, I will protect our company,
our employees, our shareholders, and you.

1056
01:27:25,955 --> 01:27:27,923
<i>I will fix this.</i>

1057
01:27:31,755 --> 01:27:34,725
<i>Francisco Francis, an eco-terrorist...</i>

1058
01:27:35,115 --> 01:27:36,924
As the majority shareholder
in ClearBec,

1059
