1083
01:30:31,155 --> 01:30:35,080
Francis is a terrorist.
You're lunatic fringe, Jack. You know that?

1084
01:30:35,395 --> 01:30:36,635
You hear me?

1085
01:30:37,715 --> 01:30:40,480
You made shit like this disappear
a hundred times.

1086
01:30:40,515 --> 01:30:43,485
