Well, we can.

1087
01:30:44,155 --> 01:30:45,645
We can, Jack!

1088
01:30:46,355 --> 01:30:48,039
Let me tell you how this is gonna work.

1089
01:30:49,555 --> 01:30:51,364
Before your skin starts to blister,

1090
01:30:51,995 --> 01:30:54,157
you're gonna smell something.

1091
01:30:54,515 --> 01:30:58,440
You're gonna smell your hair
and your eyebrows as they begin to burn.

1092
01:31:04,635 --> 01:31:06,478
Then your eyes are gonna ooze.

1093
01:31:06,955 --> 01:31:09,037
They're gonna run
like broken egg yolks.

1094
01:31:09,395 --> 01:31:13,195
I know what you did.
I saw what you did.

1095
01:31:13,635 --> 01:31:15,285
You're not...

1096
01:31:15,515 --> 01:31:16,880
You...

1097
01:31:17,915 --> 01:31:20,361
You are not better than me, Jack!

1098
01:31:20,955 --> 01:31:22,764
We are exactly alike!

1099
01:31:24,795 --> 01:31:27,560
Take a look at yourself, Jack!

1100
01:31:27,635 --> 01:31:29,922
We are exactly alike!

1101
01:31:30,995 --> 01:31:33,396
I know who you are!

1102
01:31:39,075 --> 01:31:41,476
<i>Excuse me, sir.
Did you say "golf bag"?</i>

1103
01:31:41,555 --> 01:31:44,240
You heard right,
in a golf bag outside the house.

1104
01:31:44,315 --> 01:31:45,965
His name is Doug Calder.

1105
01:31:46,035 --> 01:31:48,959
He's the man responsible
for the shoot-out today on Front Street.

1106
01:32:01,115 --> 01:32:02,446
<i>This is Jack Begosian,</i>

1107
01:32:02,515 --> 01:32:03,955
and for those of you just tuning in,

1108
01:32:03,995 --> 01:32:07,556
you are listening to
the new daytime version of <i>The Truth.</i>

1109
01:32:07,715 --> 01:32:12,198
Today I have with me,
the great honor to have Francisco Francis,

1110
01:32:12,275 --> 01:32:14,437
the founder of La Vida Campesina movement

1111
01:32:15,355 --> 01:32:18,677
who brought to light the atrocities
committed by ClearBec in Ecuador.

1112
01:32:19,195 --> 01:32:21,402
Francisco, the floor is yours.

1113
01:32:21,715 --> 01:32:23,877
Thank you for having me, Jack.

1114
01:32:24,715 --> 01:32:28,162
The reason that the ClearBec incident
is so horrible

1115
01:32:28,755 --> 01:32:32,965
is that it exposes the lengths
to which corporate interests will go

1116
01:32:32,995 --> 01:32:34,360
in order to protect themselves.

1117
01:32:35,795 --> 01:32:36,921
Absolutely.

1118
01:32:36,995 --> 01:32:38,281
We'd like to hear your thoughts.

1119
01:32:38,355 --> 01:32:39,481
Next caller, please.

1120
01:32:39,555 --> 01:32:41,478
Hello, this is Jack Begosian.
You're on the air.

1121
01:32:41,555 --> 01:32:43,603
<i>- Hi, Jack. This is Jeff.</i>
- Hello, Jeff.

1122
01:32:43,675 --> 01:32:45,115
<i>What's gonna happen to ClearBec now?</i>

1123
01:32:47,715 --> 01:32:50,924
<i>Well, Morgan Swinton
Is the major shareholder In ClearBec,</i>

1124
01:32:50,995 --> 01:32:55,080
<i>and she has promised
to pave a new moral path for the company.</i>

1125
01:32:56,395 --> 01:32:58,477
Her brother, Bruce Swinton,
has been indicted

1126
01:32:58,555 --> 01:33:00,717
for conspiracy to commit murder.

1127
01:33:00,795 --> 01:33:02,445
<i>The guy's already out on bail.</i>

1128
01:33:02,515 --> 01:33:04,085
<i>He's got all the money in the world.</i>

1129
01:33:04,155 --> 01:33:05,964
<i>You know how the system works, Jack.</i>

1130
01:33:06,035 --> 01:33:09,005
<i>No client's guilty until
they run out of money.</i>

1131
01:33:09,035 --> 01:33:11,276
Well said. Thanks for the call.

1132
01:33:11,755 --> 01:33:14,645
You know, Jack, I think
that the important thing to realize here

1133
01:33:14,675 --> 01:33:17,838
is that the water deal
in South Africa has been stopped,

1134
01:33:17,915 --> 01:33:19,644
just as it was stopped in Paraguay,

1135
01:33:19,675 --> 01:33:20,881
just as it should be stopped everywhere.

1136
01:33:20,995 --> 01:33:23,475
We are talking about a natural resource,

1137
01:33:23,555 --> 01:33:24,966
a natural resource that
should be controlled

1138
01:33:25,035 --> 01:33:26,685
by the government for the people,

1139
01:33:26,755 --> 01:33:30,646
not by the private entity whose major
interests are to maximize profit.

1140
01:33:30,715 --> 01:33:36,040
We have individuals who can't even
afford to buy a piece of bread,

1141
01:33:36,115 --> 01:33:40,962
and now they won't even be able to
afford drinking a glass of water.

1142
01:33:42,475 --> 01:33:43,761
This is something that cannot occur.

1143
01:33:43,795 --> 01:33:45,445
This is something that we have to stop.

1144
01:33:46,155 --> 01:33:49,238
You're listening
to Francisco Francis on <i>The Truth.</i>

1145
01:33:49,755 --> 01:33:51,166
Next caller.

1146
01:33:51,435 --> 01:33:54,405
<i>I just want to know
what the hell makes people like Swinton</i>

1147
01:33:54,475 --> 01:33:56,876
