1157
01:34:39,355 --> 01:34:40,916
that are difficult for us to let go of,

1158
01:34:41,675 --> 01:34:46,966
<i>surrendering control, even of the thought
that we can judge or forgive ourselves.</i>

1159
01:34:47,195 --> 01:34:49,402
All the things we've done,
the things we carry in our past,

1160
01:34:49,475 --> 01:34:52,558
they only add up to this moment.

1161
01:34:57,075 --> 01:34:58,201
Hi.

1162
01:35:01,315 --> 01:35:02,805
Where are you?

1163
01:35:04,475 --> 01:35:05,681
I'm at the lake house.

1164
01:35:05,915 --> 01:35:10,637
Even violence, non-violence itself
is not the absence of fighting the enemy.

1165
01:35:11,435 --> 01:35:15,997
