when we were kids, didn't we?

1170
01:35:34,715 --> 01:35:35,841
Yeah.

1171
01:35:37,795 --> 01:35:41,163
It's a little chilly, but
it's beautiful as ever.

1172
01:35:42,915 --> 01:35:44,724
<i>You taught me how to swim there.</i>

1173
01:35:44,795 --> 01:35:51,599
You brought light
to a situation that was in the dark.

1174
01:35:58,035 --> 01:35:59,161
Bruce, I'm on my way.

1175
01:35:59,395 --> 01:36:02,842
You've saved countless amounts of people

1176
01:36:02,875 --> 01:36:06,402
